'''哈桑·阿卜杜拉·努里'''（{{lang-ar|حسان عبد الله النوري}}，{{bd|1960年||}}）<ref>{{cite web| title=Hassan Al Nouri Curriculum Vitae| url=http://isbm-me.com/hassan-al-nouri/ Hassan Al Nouri Cirriculum Vitae| publisher=isbm-me.com| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140505034154/http://isbm-me.com/hassan-al-nouri/| archivedate=2014-05-05| accessdate=2021-01-17}}</ref>，是一名[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]政治人物，曾经竞选[[2014年敘利亞總統選舉|2014年敘利亞總統選舉]]<ref>{{cite web| title=Syria Approves 3 Candidates to Run for Presidency| url=http://www.newindianexpress.com/world/Syria-Approves-3-Candidates-to-Run-for-Presidency/2014/05/04/article2205622.ece| publisher=[[New_Indian_Express|New Indian Express]]| accessdate=2014-06-05| archive-date=2014-05-05| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140505044854/http://www.newindianexpress.com/world/Syria-Approves-3-Candidates-to-Run-for-Presidency/2014/05/04/article2205622.ece| dead-url=no}}</ref>，获得4.3%的选票。

他曾经在{{link-en|沃伦国立大学|Warren National University}}获得博士学位，不过这是一所未认证的[[野鸡大学|野鸡大学]]，2009年被迫关闭<ref>[http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2014/06/02/the_biggest_losers_syria_assad_presidential_election "The Biggest Losers"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2014/06/02/the_biggest_losers_syria_assad_presidential_election |date=20140605190447 }} [[Foreign_Policy|Foreign Policy]]</ref>。他曾经担任叙利亚国会议员以及行政发展部部长，现在是一名商人<ref>{{cite news|title=叙大选首现多党派竞选 其他候选人均支持巴沙尔|url=http://roll.sohu.com/20140604/n400423555.shtml|accessdate=2014-06-05|newspaper=搜狐网|archive-date=2014-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140607002856/http://roll.sohu.com/20140604/n400423555.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

